{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":78,"arabicnumber":78,"text":"حدثنا عبد الله بن محمد النفيلي، حدثنا وكيع، عن اسامة بن زيد، عن ابن خربوذ، عن ام صبية الجهنية، قالت اختلفت يدي ويد رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم في الوضوء من اناء واحد","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":78}}]}